pull_request.title: Enable hybrid auth in TLS 1.3
pull_request.body:
Enable hybrid auth in TLS 1.3 by defining naive hybrid schemes (parallel signatures; concatenated serialization of artifacts), combining p256/rsa3072 with L1 schemes, and p384 with L3 schemes.
